title: Fruit Bats - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Fruit Bats performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded May 26, 2023

Songs:
Rushin’ River Valley
Waking Up in Los Angeles
The Bottom of It
We Used to Live Here

Eric D. Johnson - Vocals, Guitar, Piano
Josh Mease - Guitar
David Dawda - Bass
Josh Adams - Drums
Frank LoCrasto - Piano, Synth

Host: Cheryl Waters
Audio Engineers: Jon Roberts, Julian Martlew
Audio Mixer: Nathan Vanderpool
Mastering: Matt Ogaz
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Alaia D’Alessandro, Scott Holpainen
Editor: Alaia D’Alessandro
